OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening, although some rain in
OL,7,Fthe west later. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fwill spread to most places during the
OL,9,Fearly hours. A mild night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with some
OL,12,Foccasional rain or drizzle, perhaps
OL,13,Fturning more persistent for a time
OL,14,Fearlier in the morning. Drier and
OL,15,Fbrighter with a few showers through
OL,16,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
