OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FUnsettled with showers or longer
OL,7,Fspells of rain on Thursday. Brighter
OL,8,Fwith a few showers on Friday. Further
OL,9,Frain spreading east on Saturday.
